data.text:
The One With Phoebe's Husband

Phoebe has married a gay Canadian ice dancer to help him get his green card.

Won't You Be Our Neighbour

Phil and Claire are less than enthusiastic while meeting their new obnoxious neighbours. Jay learns that Manny's new girlfriend is also his former business partner's granddaughter.

Halloween 3 - Awesomeland

Phil takes over Claire's annual Halloween in order to make a fest of his own. Jay refuses to wear a Shrek costume that Gloria bought for him, preferring to be Prince Charming instead.

The Big Guns

Claire is furious about neighbours Ronnie and Amber's eyesore of a boat on their front lawn and it soon becomes an all-out war when Phil calls in the big guns as back up.

Knock 'Em Down

Jay agrees to sub in on Cam's bowling team for the finals, but Cam was not fully upfront about it being an all gay league, which puts Jay in a precarious position.
